<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كُوِّرَتْ}</span> ... لُفَّتْ، وَذَهَبَ ضَوْؤُهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{انكَدَرَتْ}</span> ... تَنَاثَرَتْ، وَذَهَبَ نُورُهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُيِّرَتْ}</span> ... أُزِيلَتْ عَنْ وَجْهِ الأَرْضِ؛ فَصَارَتْ هَبَاءً مَنْثُورًا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْعِشَارُ}</span> ... النُّوقُ الحَوَامِلُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عُطِّلَتْ}</span> ... أُهْمِلَتْ، وَتُرِكَتْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حُشِرَتْ}</span> ... جُمِعَتْ، وَاخْتَلَطَتْ؛ لِيُقْتَصَّ لِبَعْضِهَا مِنْ بَعْضٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُجِّرَتْ}</span> ... مُلِئَتْ حَتَّى خَاضَتْ، فَانْفَجَرَت، ثُمَّ اتَّقَدَتْ نِيرَانًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{زُوِّجَتْ}</span> ... قُرِنَتْ بِأَمْثَالِهَا وَنَظَائِرِهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمَوْؤُودَةُ}</span> ... الطِّفْلَةُ المَدْفُونَةُ حَيَّةً.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الصُّحُفُ}</span> ... صُحُفُ الأَعْمَالِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نُشِرَتْ}</span> ... فُتِحَتْ، وَبُسِطَتْ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كُشِطَتْ}</span> ... قُلِعَتْ، وَأُزِيلَتْ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُعِّرَتْ}</span> ... أُوقِدَتْ، فَأُضْرِمَتْ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُزْلِفَتْ}</span> ... قُرِّبَتْ مِنْ أَهْلِهَا.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَحْضَرَتْ}</span> ... قَدَّمَتْ مِنْ خَيْرٍ أَوْ شَرٍّ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
